spec_data.Name: ogre-samples
spec_data.License: MIT with exceptions and CC-BY-SA and Freely redistributable without restriction
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the compiled (not the source) sample applications coming
with Ogre.  It also contains some media (meshes, textures,...) needed by these
samples. The samples are installed in /usr/lib64/Samples/*.so and can be run
using SampleBrowser.
